
     NAME
          icclose - close a 'ic'-formatted file 

     FORTRAN F77 SPECIFICATION
          integer function  icclose(iu)
          integer*4 iu

     PARAMETERS

          INPUT:
          iu    = file unit, can range from 1 to 25

     RETURNS
          0     = everything fine 

     DESCRIPTION
          iclose closes a file that has been opend by icopen(3) 
          for reading and writing with icwrite(3), icread(3).
          For a short description of the alogorithm see ictools(3).

